content:
Move Excerpts Within an Einstein Conversation Mining Report

You can move excerpts into a contact reason to create your dataset.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Einstein Conversation Mining is available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience with the Service Intelligence add-on. Setup for Einstein Conversation Mining is available in Lightning Experience.
Available in: Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

Select a report and click the summary name of a topic.
Select some excerpts, and then click Move Excerpts.
Select your topic for the excerpts.
Select your contact reason group. Use the dropdown to select a contact reason, or click New Contact Reason to add a contact reason. After you click New Contact Reason, a text box replaces the dropdown to enter your new contact reason name.
Save your changes.
title: Configuring Einstein Conversation Mining in Service Cloud
